{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"James Ford","author":"James Ford"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"5f05befe-70f7-5977-8a3a-ff362ec48212","html":"<p>Well, I'm a bit slack on the whole updates front - ImageSizer 0.4.0 and 0.4.1 have already slipped under the radar without a blog post - but with the latest release I thought I'd draw a little attention to it, not least because it fixes a bit an annoying bug that I introduced in version 0.4.1!</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5457dafc4a3e45a32d5622bda5b49d54/48a11/imagesizer042.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 500px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 55.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"ImageSizer 0.4.2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/5457dafc4a3e45a32d5622bda5b49d54/48a11/imagesizer042.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5457dafc4a3e45a32d5622bda5b49d54/3b5c6/imagesizer042.jpg 158w,\n/static/5457dafc4a3e45a32d5622bda5b49d54/434a1/imagesizer042.jpg 315w,\n/static/5457dafc4a3e45a32d5622bda5b49d54/48a11/imagesizer042.jpg 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h3>So, what's new in the latest version?</h3>\n<p>Well, one of the things that I've found a lot of AIR applications are missing at the moment, is the ability to configure their settings - particulary those things mentioned by Serge Jespers in his post: <strong>\"6 AIR features that may annoy your users\"</strong> [<a href=\"http://www.webkitchen.be/2008/12/17/best-practices-6-air-features-that-may-annoy-your-users/\">link</a>].  Back with version 0.3.10 I introduced some Pixel Bender filters to the application.  Version 0.4 introduced the Application Settings window - although it only appeared to work.  Version 0.4.1 expanded on this by introducing some backend code that actually stored the settings, but had a glaring typo that meant the whole thing didn't work.  Version 0.4.2 in short, fixes this.</p>\n<h3>So, what settings have we introduced?</h3>\n<p><strong>Remembering window position and dimensions;</strong>\n<strong><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/46a0dbb1b7db706b2c3fde85846e84cc/48a11/imagesizerpreferences.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 500px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"ImageSizer - Window Preferences\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/46a0dbb1b7db706b2c3fde85846e84cc/48a11/imagesizerpreferences.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/46a0dbb1b7db706b2c3fde85846e84cc/3b5c6/imagesizerpreferences.jpg 158w,\n/static/46a0dbb1b7db706b2c3fde85846e84cc/434a1/imagesizerpreferences.jpg 315w,\n/static/46a0dbb1b7db706b2c3fde85846e84cc/48a11/imagesizerpreferences.jpg 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>Visual Effects;</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/62f899195802cbd120dadc974a804d16/48a11/imagesizervisualeffects.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 500px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"ImageSizer - Visual Effects\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/62f899195802cbd120dadc974a804d16/48a11/imagesizervisualeffects.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/62f899195802cbd120dadc974a804d16/3b5c6/imagesizervisualeffects.jpg 158w,\n/static/62f899195802cbd120dadc974a804d16/434a1/imagesizervisualeffects.jpg 315w,\n/static/62f899195802cbd120dadc974a804d16/48a11/imagesizervisualeffects.jpg 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>Automatic Updates;</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a5c8c3b268ed28753962cd464b55668c/48a11/imagesizerautomaticupdates.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 500px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"ImageSizer - Automatic Updates\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/a5c8c3b268ed28753962cd464b55668c/48a11/imagesizerautomaticupdates.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a5c8c3b268ed28753962cd464b55668c/3b5c6/imagesizerautomaticupdates.jpg 158w,\n/static/a5c8c3b268ed28753962cd464b55668c/434a1/imagesizerautomaticupdates.jpg 315w,\n/static/a5c8c3b268ed28753962cd464b55668c/48a11/imagesizerautomaticupdates.jpg 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></strong></p>\n<h3>Download ImageSizer 0.4.2</h3>\n<p><object width=\"215\" height=\"180\" data=\"/airapps/AIRInstallBadge.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\"><param name=\"flashvars\" value=\"airversion=1.5&amp;appname=ImageSizer&amp;appurl=http://psyked.co.uk/airapps/ImageSizer042.air&amp;appid=couk.psyked.ImageSizer&amp;pubid=07510AB144CCA2FB1C33EE50283E9A7AD43F7966.1&amp;appversion=0.4.2&amp;titlecolor=#339999\" /><param name=\"src\" value=\"/airapps/AIRInstallBadge.swf\" /></object></p>\n<h3>Known issues:</h3>\n<p>Unfortunately, no sooner than I'd released this version, I noticed another problem with it.  Or potential problem with it.  I haven't built in any defaults to the application.  So my clever code to enable users to turn off the automatic updates now means that - because there's no settings existing - the automatic updates will be turned off.  Ideally, it should remain turned on!  Darn those logical errors!</p>\n<p>My next things to explore are <strong>\"Start on Login\"</strong>, <strong>\"System Tray/Dock Icons\"</strong> and <strong>\"Google Analytics tracking\"</strong>.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Introducing ImageSizer 0.4.2","date":"January 20, 2009","tags":["imagesizer"],"url":null,"image":null,"description":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"prev":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/blog/geocoding-uk-postcodes-with-google-map-api/","tags":["google-maps"],"title":"Geocoding UK Postcodes with Google Map API","date":"2009-01-20T10:55:49.000Z","description":null,"image":null}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/blog/auto-shapes-for-defraga/","tags":["flex","degrafa","drawing-api"],"title":"Auto shapes for Degrafa","date":"2009-01-22T10:52:14.000Z","description":null,"image":null}}}}